00:13:59.446 --> 00:14:00.996 A:middle
audio on the Watch requires

00:14:01.046 --> 00:14:02.796 A:middle
headphones or an external

00:14:02.796 --> 00:14:05.276 A:middle
speaker to be connected just as

00:14:05.276 --> 00:14:06.336 A:middle
when playing from the built-in

00:14:06.336 --> 00:14:06.746 A:middle
music app.

00:14:08.256 --> 00:14:09.646 A:middle
For this reason, Bluetooth

00:14:09.646 --> 00:14:11.106 A:middle
routing is part of the session

00:14:11.186 --> 00:14:12.316 A:middle
activation process.

00:14:12.526 --> 00:14:13.686 A:middle
If you set your route sharing

00:14:13.686 --> 00:14:15.486 A:middle
policy to longform, as you

00:14:16.236 --> 00:14:18.136 A:middle
should, will automatically

00:14:18.136 --> 00:14:19.796 A:middle
connect to the headphones with

00:14:19.796 --> 00:14:21.536 A:middle
Apple wireless chip, like

00:14:21.536 --> 00:14:24.296 A:middle
AirPods or Beats Studio3, if

00:14:24.296 --> 00:14:25.086 A:middle
they're already in use.

00:14:25.706 --> 00:14:27.336 A:middle
Or, will show a route picker to

00:14:27.336 --> 00:14:28.776 A:middle
let the user choose other

00:14:28.776 --> 00:14:30.376 A:middle
headphones or Bluetooth speakers

00:14:30.776 --> 00:14:32.346 A:middle
when you call the activate with

00:14:32.346 --> 00:14:33.846 A:middle
options completion API in a

00:14:33.846 --> 00:14:34.916 A:middle
session that's new.

00:14:38.266 --> 00:14:39.886 A:middle
You could also use the MP now

00:14:39.886 --> 00:14:41.496 A:middle
playing info center API to

00:14:41.566 --> 00:14:42.996 A:middle
populate the now playing app

00:14:43.596 --> 00:14:44.846 A:middle
with information about what your

00:14:44.846 --> 00:14:45.636 A:middle
app is playing.

00:14:46.036 --> 00:14:47.846 A:middle
Which means your apps info will

00:14:47.846 --> 00:14:49.136 A:middle
show in the now playing

00:14:49.306 --> 00:14:49.986 A:middle
complication.

00:14:53.326 --> 00:14:54.476 A:middle
And you can handle the media

00:14:54.476 --> 00:14:55.746 A:middle
remote commands that make sense

00:14:55.746 --> 00:14:57.496 A:middle
for your app; from play and

00:14:57.496 --> 00:15:00.366 A:middle
pause, to next and previous, to

